thunar-volman: thunar-volman (Volume Manager for Thunar)
thunar-volman:
thunar-volman: The Thunar Volume Manager is an extension for the Thunar file manager,
thunar-volman: which enables automatic management of removable drives and media. For
thunar-volman: example, if thunar-volman is installed and configured properly, and
thunar-volman: you plug in your digital camera, it will automatically launch your
thunar-volman: preferred photo application and import the new pictures from the
thunar-volman: camera into your photo collection.
thunar-volman: http://goodies.xfce.org/projects/thunar-plugins/thunar-volman
